body: Wow, someone actually called out the all-but-ubiquitous notion that semen is bitter. It's not salty either,  by the way

This is probably the most believable, well executed futa manga I've read till now. I get that it all comes down to some1 revealing her penis and that leads to sex. 

The thing that always bothers me is that with most I've read go into the action with no build up in the second page, pretty much any ruining any attempts at telling a story.

This one gets it perfectly right with the girl randomly growing a dick and panicking about it, instead of going full horndog on us, she doesn't want it till her buttons are pushed which I find believable. With her friend(now lover) being curious yet cautious about it and turns on her friend accidentally which is also believable.
